data.description: ASSUMABLE VA Mortgage! WOW, 3.5%! Seller says bring All offers! This exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence awaits its lucky new owners. Boasting 2,050 square feet of pure luxury and positioned on a sprawling one-acre oasis, this home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and tranquil countryside living. Step inside, and be greeted by a spacious open-concept layout that beckons you to unwind. Four generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for your family or guests. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, offering a private retreat with a en-suite bath. As you step outside, you'll discover a breathtaking, one-acre paradise surrounded by a sturdy fence, offering privacy and     security for your loved ones. Marvel at the majestic grandfather oaks that grace the landscape, providing shade and an enchanting backdrop to your outdoor gatherings. This charming abode is situated on a paved road in a peaceful neighborhood, ensuring easy access to city amenities while preserving the tranquility of a rural escape. Whether you're enjoying a cup of morning coffee on the front porch or hosting a barbecue in the expansive backyard, you'll relish the serenity and space this property offers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this slice of paradise your own! Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the epitome of comfortable, countryside living. Your dream home awaits!
